Package com.kicas.rp.data

Class Deserializer

java.lang.Object
com.kicas.rp.data.Deserializer
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class Deserializer extends Object implements AutoCloseable
Deserializes plugin data files, including regions.dat and playerdata.dat. The methods and order of read operations in this class are meant to mirror those in the Serializer class. The Serializer class is considered to be "always right" and this class must conform to it and previous versions of it.
